{"tid":1486050,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非極致］今個星期五係香港再上國際舞台千載難逢嘅機會","createTime":"2019-08-18T18:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:56:02.000Z","uid":112094,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c83d53d74a2fcaef62b90df502ef7541d73fc8","tid":1486050,"uid":112094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打開post講過，不過沉咗底，我再開post<br />\n<br />\nTLDR:<br />\n<br />\n星期五放工後一齊去唔同地鐵站出口，向前後一個站方向組人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知今個星期五係咩日子？係<span style=\"color: red;\">波羅的海之路三十周年</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，二戰時期希特拉同斯大林秘密簽定協議將波羅的海三小國（立陶宛、拉脫維亞和愛沙尼亞）劃入蘇聯勢力範圍，經過長年抗爭，三個國家嘅人民喺當年蘇聯嘅民主化浪潮中發起一次組人鏈嘅活動。<br />\n<br />\n喺1989年8月23號傍晚七點，組成超過650公里嘅人鏈連接三個國家嘅首都，以抗議蘇聯嘅非法佔領。<span style=\"color: red;\">媒體爭相報導呢次抗爭，更直接導致波羅的海三國率先脫離蘇聯加盟國身分獨立，算係和理非成功爭取嘅一例。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今個星期五就係8月23號</span>，時間嚟到三十年後嘅香港，過去兩個月抗爭揭露中共港共打壓香港人嘅殘暴一面，如果我哋要以受害人身分向國際求助，就需要非常上鏡吸引報導嘅抗爭手法，仲可以連結多三個國家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n具體做法：星期五放工後一齊去唔同地鐵站出口，向前後一個站方向組人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期五放工後一齊去唔同地鐵站出口，向前後一個站方向組人鏈<br />\n<br />\n港島線：沿電車路<br />\n荃灣線：彌敦道駁長沙灣道再上荔景去荃灣<br />\n觀塘線：龍翔道駁觀塘道<br />\n<br />\n好處：方便/ 和平 / 冇咁阻街/ 有影響力/ 畫面靚/ 接觸面廣/ 參與度高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東歐國家、蘇聯國內和臺灣都相繼舉行過類似示威，如2004年約有200萬臺灣民眾參與的228百萬人手牽手護台灣。<br />\n<br />\n連2016年周融都試過號召五千人上山頂，喺太平山頂手牽手，參加「正能量　團結太平山」活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook post<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156092700521504&amp;id=507126503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156092700521504%26id%3D507126503&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=4c20283e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156092700521504&amp;id=507126503</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9ef4157b3a49ac0f3e48dbd1759767791e607e5","tid":1486050,"uid":2310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"d20277e834ae8826ed63ddeea20c81e20ea518c1","tid":1486050,"uid":266170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Flag_of_Estonia.svg/800px-Flag_of_Estonia.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8f%2FFlag_of_Estonia.svg%2F800px-Flag_of_Estonia.svg.png&h=59fcad4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/84/Flag_of_Latvia.svg/1920px-Flag_of_Latvia.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F84%2FFlag_of_Latvia.svg%2F1920px-Flag_of_Latvia.svg.png&h=d5dd1a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Flag_of_Lithuania.svg/1920px-Flag_of_Lithuania.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"